room_title: Escape room "SEAL Team" by Escape Tactic in Charlotte
room_description: You and your unit are part of America’s elite SEAL team. You’ve been assigned a classified top-secret mission to eliminate a high-value terrorist target thought to be hiding in the streets of Kabul. After being dropped into the city by helicopter, you must locate the target’s hideout, navigate through extensive security measures and booby traps to enter the building, and ultimately eliminate the terrorist threat before he escapes your grasp.
